extendedInfo.description: Bank with Community Bank anywhere you like. Our CellTeller app makes it easy to check your balances on the go - as well as, pay bills and locate Community Bank offices.  CellTeller is free to all Community Bank customers who have accounts opened in Mississippi, Alabama, Tennessee, and Florida.Features:â¢Check Account Balancesâ¢Transfer funds between accountsâ¢Pay Bills**â¢Find our ATMs and Banking Centers using the GPS system provided by your Android.***â¢View check images*Must be an Online Banking Customer**Online customers must first setup transfer and bill pay accounts prior to using these features.***This is limited to locating our banking centers and ATMs. Please refer to your carrier for any fees that may apply.

reviews.title: Version 2.0
reviews.comment: The new UI is pretty much like before which is a good thing. No need to change anything that\'s not broken. Everything works well in this update. Love how I have access to all my bank statements for quick viewing. Is it possible to have an alert when we receive a new e-statement? Great app considering the small user base.

reviews.title: App is good but extremely slow
reviews.comment: Even on Wifi the app takes nearly 5 minutes to process through all the logging in and over to the transactions.
